      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/535682644_18516711967056563_6719837684086995402_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcwMjg0NDQxNDg0MDgyMTkxMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=_ilY3Bxmw_AQ7kNvwFFCird&amp;_nc_oc=AdrpUmU0GW6tU97UAZgTX_9BkU3-p-TIauekVOCWa684jMeDG6ljDjcD-urtBS2nGdQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=wc83WhiONr6KNzCigBkXSg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyzqHTDjQRhmt3mz3_4LBlq2OGwu_WufgsaqLkcf0U21A&amp;oe=69C8ED1F" alt="Instagram billede fra @andersdalhoej" /></p><p><strong>@andersdalhoej</strong></p><p>There should ultimately be room for all of us 🖤<br/>
<br/>
I appreciate all the people who joined pride 2025 for their own reasons - and everyone who joined in on the conversation on where k🖤nk belongs compared to pride 🖤 There is a lot of political things to talk about as well, but for this little series it’s about the Manifest CPH community</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/535682644_18516711967056563_6719837684086995402_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_p1080x1080_sh2.08_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=106&amp;ig_cache_key=MzcwMjg0NDQxNDg0MDgyMTkxMQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjE0NDB4MTgwMC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=_ilY3Bxmw_AQ7kNvwFFCird&amp;_nc_oc=AdrpUmU0GW6tU97UAZgTX_9BkU3-p-TIauekVOCWa684jMeDG6ljDjcD-urtBS2nGdQ&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=wc83WhiONr6KNzCigBkXSg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyzqHTDjQRhmt3mz3_4LBlq2OGwu_WufgsaqLkcf0U21A&amp;oe=69C8ED1F" alt="Instagram billede fra @andersdalhoej" /></p><p><strong>@andersdalhoej</strong></p><p>There should ultimately be room for all of us 🖤<br/>
<br/>
I appreciate all the people who joined pride 2025 for their own reasons - and everyone who joined in on the conversation on where k🖤nk belongs compared to pride 🖤 There is a lot of political things to talk about as well, but for this little series it’s about the Manifest CPH community</p>]]></content:encoded>
