      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/643008122_17922453057257901_253476469465950128_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQ5NjI1MzczOTU5NTcxNjQ1Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=s4lUtjPbdusQ7kNvwFx_94l&amp;_nc_oc=AdptDKmDecUVRipC8GSbkjA3JG9Jp2yfNorcawVKBA5AYOrmGxuXXIrB41NjDE3HHyw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=wc83WhiONr6KNzCigBkXSg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afxq90u2-d3ze3mlBakEC42Z-P5Hq6kmen0O81oYJYmirQ&amp;oe=69C8EEFE" alt="Instagram billede fra @andersdalhoej" /></p><p><strong>@andersdalhoej</strong></p><p>As a celebration of @frida.retz pregnancy and her art, we decided to spend and creative evening capturing eachothers style and expression in a unity - ended up as this series 🤍 Thank you for letting me capture this episode of your life - and congrats with your baby 👏🏻</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/643008122_17922453057257901_253476469465950128_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=MzQ5NjI1MzczOTU5NTcxNjQ1Mg%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTM1MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=s4lUtjPbdusQ7kNvwFx_94l&amp;_nc_oc=AdptDKmDecUVRipC8GSbkjA3JG9Jp2yfNorcawVKBA5AYOrmGxuXXIrB41NjDE3HHyw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=wc83WhiONr6KNzCigBkXSg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_Afxq90u2-d3ze3mlBakEC42Z-P5Hq6kmen0O81oYJYmirQ&amp;oe=69C8EEFE" alt="Instagram billede fra @andersdalhoej" /></p><p><strong>@andersdalhoej</strong></p><p>As a celebration of @frida.retz pregnancy and her art, we decided to spend and creative evening capturing eachothers style and expression in a unity - ended up as this series 🤍 Thank you for letting me capture this episode of your life - and congrats with your baby 👏🏻</p>]]></content:encoded>
